headline: Positive Trial Data on Evolut TAVR Likely to Support MDT Stock
summary: At the CRT conference 2025, Medtronic presented two-year favorable SMART trial data, which demonstrated the superior performance of the Evolut TAVR valve in patients with AS.

headline: 2 Reasons to Like BSX (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Since March 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 97.5%. But one standout stock has nearly doubled the market - over the past five years, Boston Scientific has surged 176% to $97 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 16.8% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 13%.
